author: Humphrey Hawkins
title: Humphrey Hawkins
text: I found the glasses i was after at a 25% discount to the price at my local sunglass store. They delivered them from italy to Australia in under a week. FAR superior performance to my experience with iframes, who took nearly 2 months before advising me they couldn't actually deliver the glasses I'd bought. Otticanet all the way
